item.title: Jaipur police rescued Anuj, a
item.description: Jaipur police rescued Anuj, a man kidnapped from Rajasthan and held hostage in a hotel in Himachal Pradesh. The dramatic operation saw five suspects arrested. Kidnappers had abducted Anuj on August 18 after mistaking him for being wealthy. A video captured officers reassuring Anuj during the rescue. #JaipurPolice #HimachalPradesh
